============================================================
公共領域方法論引用 (Public Domain Methodologies)
============================================================

本工具包使用以下公共領域的商業與設計方法論：
- Porter's Five Forces (Michael Porter, 1979)
- SWOT Analysis
- Business Model Canvas (Alexander Osterwalder, 2010)
- Design Thinking / How Might We (IDEO)
- TAM/SAM/SOM Market Sizing
- User Persona & Empathy Map (UX methodology)
- Crazy 8's Ideation (Google Ventures Design Sprint)

這些方法論為廣泛使用的公共知識，不屬於任何特定授權。

